Aim:
    To Create a React based website for your client using components, elements and styles.
Description:
    This project is a React.js-based website designed for a client, offering a modern and responsive
user experience. The website is built using components like Header, Footer, Navbar, About, Services, and
Contact, which makes it easy to manage and reuse sections. Common elements such as buttons, cards, and forms
are created for consistency across the site. CSS styling ensures a clean and attractive design that works on 
desktops, tablets, and mobile devices. Navigation between pages is handled with React Router, and interactive
features like contact forms and dynamic sections enhance user engagement. Overall, the website is easy to maintain,
scalable, and professional-looking, providing a strong online presence for the client.

Coding:
